{"about_the_game":"\n\t\t\t\t\t<p><i>Ben There, Dan That!</i> and <i>Time Gentlemen, Please!</i> are a couple of rip-roaring point-and-click adventure games . With tongue firmly in cheek, sit back, relax, and put your mind to work solving puzzles, and reading some very funny dialogue. It's like a book, only good!</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>From an horrific and untimely death in deep, dark Peru, via preposterous-and-suspect alien invasions, to whipping back-and-forth in time to stop Hitler and his army of robot Nazi dinosaur clones, this is one set of adventures you're unlikely to forget.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Key features:</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>Funny words that'll actually probably make you laugh out loud!\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>Graphics AND sound effects!\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>Thousands of unique responses for almost every action you can think of!\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>NAZI  DINOSAURS!\n\t\t\t\t\t","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/37400/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1447352433","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/37400/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1447352433","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/37400/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1447352433","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/37400/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1447352433","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":37410,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"\n\t\t\t\t\t<p><i>Ben There, Dan That!</i> and <i>Time Gentlemen, Please!</i> are a couple of rip-roaring point-and-click adventure games . With tongue firmly in cheek, sit back, relax, and put your mind to work solving puzzles, and reading some very funny dialogue. It's like a book, only good!</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>From an horrific and untimely death in deep, dark Peru, via preposterous-and-suspect 